#### With loading state

This technique is useful if you need to show a loading state, to avoid the resizing and shifting of the buttons:


<?php start="demo-block" classicComponentId="components/button-set/partials/code/code-snippets/button-set-loading.classic" gtsComponentId="components/button-set/partials/code/code-snippets/button-set-loading" hbs="&lt;Hds::ButtonSet &#123;&#123;style width=&quot;15rem&quot;&#125;&#125;&gt;
