  &lt;Hds::Button @text=&quot;Cancel&quot; @color=&quot;secondary&quot; @isFullWidth=&#123;&#123;true&#125;&#125; &#123;&#123;on &quot;click&quot; this.cancelLoading&#125;&#125; /&gt;
